p: The envelope sequences of the DENV-1 isolates analyzed in this study are in GenBank under the following accession numbers: KT438562, KT438564, KT438565, KT438566, KT438567, KT438568, KT438569, KT438570, KT438571, KT438572, KT438573, KT438574, KT438575, KT438576, KT438577, KT438578, KT438579, KT438581, KT438582 and KT438583. Additional genomic sequences used in the aa substitutions analysis can be found as GenBank: KP188543 and KP188540.
